which is going to take centuries to complete,

14:06.460 --> 14:10.240
I know you were a history major, is there any kind of historical precedent

14:10.240 --> 14:13.120
for that on a much smaller scale that gave you the idea?

14:14.120 --> 14:16.940
No, not at all. The idea itself

14:19.140 --> 14:21.360
here I'm really trying to think back

14:21.360 --> 14:25.020
because the individual suggestions you get when you're

14:26.640 --> 14:29.100
thinking about trying to start a story

14:29.100 --> 14:33.080
and you're gathering in the hooks and suggestions that pop

14:33.080 --> 14:37.320
up can be so minor that I'm just

14:37.320 --> 14:41.140
trying to think back and I can't really remember any similar historical

14:42.060 --> 14:44.660
parallel although I'm sure it's been tried

